### Security — never commit these ###
# RSA private/public key files — the private key can decrypt all
# Aadhaar/PAN/KYC data. If this leaks, all encrypted data is compromised.
rsa-keys/

# Uploaded KYC documents (encrypted at rest, but still shouldn't live in git)
uploads/

# Any local secrets/env files
.env
application-local.properties
application-secrets.properties